Using a package repository
(x) Go to ... https://packagecloud.io/Lazin/Akumuli
(x) Select ... Debian & Manual Installation
(x) Refresh local package cache ... sudo apt-get update
(x) Ensure required tools ... 
    $> sudo apt-get install curl gnupg apt-transport-https
(x) Install the GPG key that used to sign the repoistory ... 
    $> curl -L https://packagecloud.io/Lazin/Akumuli.gpgkey | sudo apt-key add -

